<seg id="593">- Large-scale taxable companies shall refrain from registering from USt to be paid in § 21 (1) CZ UStG.</seg>
<seg id="594">Germany: There are no regulations at federal level.</seg>
<seg id="595">Accordingly, the statistics for auditors and USt special auditors compiled at federal level do not provide such information.</seg>
