<seg id="597">However, the Federal Central Office for Taxes can evaluate the ZAUBER database, to enter the tax additional result achieved by them in the event of exceeding a certain threshold in the auditors and tax traders of the countries.</seg>
<seg id="598">• Does the financial administration analyse results-related audit fields and draw consequences for strategic control?</seg>
<seg id="599">CZ: Yes, e.g. nationwide tests are carried out in terms of risk-free goods and industries.</seg>
<seg id="600">Germany: There are no regulations at federal level.</seg>
